title: Bathory (Full Discography)
description:
I have been waiting to upload Bathory, until now! This is all of Bathory's studio albums. Compilations, Demo's & Tributes not included. Enjoy!
This torrent consists of these albums:

1984 - Batory

1985 - The Return

1987 - Under the Sign of the Black Mark

1988 - Blood Fire Death

1990 - Hammerheart

1991 - Twillight of the Gods

1994 - Requiem

1995 - Octagon

1996 - Blood on Ice (Recorded 1989)

2001 - Destroyer of Worlds

2002 - Nordland I

2003 - Nordland II
